nodes.title: Lora Randomizer
widgets_values:
This will only work with the Promt Control Nodes

You still can choose a specific lora:

- Use the Promitive Noder to select the desired LORA
- switch "control after generate" to fixed

Use control after generate to only load LORAS with a specific String:

i.e. if you have a Folder Named "IL_Best_Styles" just enter this into the "control after generate" and it will only choose files in this Folder or Files with the same String.

You can set the weight Range with the FL Random Numer Node

nodes.title: TIPO Settings
widgets_values:
TIPO Format Settings:

<|special|>, 
<|characters|>, <|copyrights|>, 
<|artist|>, 

<|general|>,

<|extended|>.

<|quality|>, <|meta|>, <|rating|>

Prompt Format: The format of final prompt. Default value is the recommended format of Kohaku XL Zeta. To be placed in TIPO Format:

    <|special|>: 1girl, 1boy, 1other, ...
    <|characters|>: character tags
    <|copyrights|>: copyright tags (series name)
    <|artist|>: artist tags
    <|general|>: general tags
    <|meta|>: highres/lowres/absurdres are all meta tags
    <|quality|>: score_xxx, masterpiece, best quality...
    <|rating|>: safe, sensitive, nsfw, explicit ...
    <|generated|>: generated NL prompt - add this if you want a Natural Language Prompt
    <|extended|>: extended NL prompt
